title: Youth unemployment rate in Egypt in 2019
summary: In general Youth unemployment rate has rose over the Year.
Youth unemployment rate is slightly increasing from 2001 to 2003, roughly constant from 2003 to 2004, and finally slightly increasing from 2004 to 2005.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2002 and 2003.
The highest Youth unemployment rate, of value 31.18 was reached at Year 2005
Minimum Youth unemployment rate about 26.23 was reached at Year 2002
